---
title: Honey Mustard Pork Steaks with Cheesy Chive Mash
description: Add some flair to your usual meat and three with these sweet honey mustard-glazed pork steaks. Along with a silky herbed mash, it'll be tough deciding what the best part of this quick and easy dish is!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/5dba338163e39d51e602213b-6c1c2b13.jpg
